desc_short	-----								Enter the deadly game show of Man in a Maze and leave with more than your life! Sneak past patrolling robots, avoid deadly traps and fight back with nifty gadgets and weapons. Man in a Maze has elements of puzzle, arcade and stealth – plus local multiplayer for 2-4 players.							
